{"tid":755531,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔獸世界》暗影之月聯盟新香港公會招人","createTime":"2018-07-25T09:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T01:16:43.000Z","uid":172454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7766d4f1b70781b2b3f15166b94097e96d6ab203","tid":755531,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"為迎接魔獸世界新版本《決戰艾澤拉斯》即將於 8 月 14 日上市，希望籍此招募所有有興趣既新手或老手一齊玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://worldofwarcraft.com/zh-tw/battle-for-azeroth\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworldofwarcraft.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fbattle-for-azeroth&h=06b66ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jSJr3dXZfcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjSJr3dXZfcg&d=ldkSIQ05jxfPpNtjU%2FieMy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=82a93505\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jSJr3dXZfcg</a><br />\n<br />\n伺服器：台服　暗影之月／眾星之子／語風<br />\n陣營　：聯盟<br />\n公會　：Essence<br />\n公會簡介：本公會原身為水晶之刺部落老牌香港公會，曾為台服最大香港公會之一。<br />\n經歷浩劫與重生、潘達利亞之謎、德拉諾之霸、軍臨天下版本，現在最新版本決戰艾澤拉斯創立暗影之月聯盟分會，希望匯聚香港聯盟玩家一同享受遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n公會方向：暫會以半休閒公會形式運行，初期目標建立一團１０－２０人副本固定團，並定期舉辦公會休閒副本活動。<br />\n公會FB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WoWHKEssence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWoWHKEssence%2F&d=ldkSIQ05jxfPpNtjU%2FieMy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b9049834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WoWHKEssence/</a><br />\n公會Youtube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/HKEssence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FHKEssence&d=ldkSIQ05jxfPpNtjU%2FieMy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9fce8a17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/HKEssence</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友可以ADD：<br />\nBNET：syicheung#4357<br />\nTelegram：HKEssence<br />\n<br />\n無論你係PVE/PVP向，新手/老手，專業/休閒玩家，只要你有興趣玩，只要你係香港人，快Ｄ加入啦！"},{"pid":"1fde16983d07c917099cceed77ef4189b89b3a74","tid":75553